Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Star comedian Matsumoto’s first tweet is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.75,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Here’s Mr. Matsumoto’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.01,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,{\pos(517,340)}Mine is normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.00,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Here it is.  “I have debuted.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:32.41,[Rola],,0,0,0,,That’s so ordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.09,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,I don’t know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn’t good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.99,[Rola],,0,0,0,,That’s no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.74,[Rola],,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.13,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,No, {\alpha&HFF&\t(250,200,\alpha&H00&)\fs40}no, {\alpha&HFF&\t(500,200,\alpha&H00&\fs44)}no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.93,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,I don’t understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.76,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:50.90,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,{\move(232,215,150,333,750,0)\fs2\t(0,700,\fs34)}Ah!~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:52.76,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,{\move(150,333,450,500,900,0)\fs34}Ah!~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.70,[Matsumoto],typeset,0,0,0,,Then what do we do? What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After the panicking Matsumoto, Mimura’s first tweet is:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:04.65,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Let’s look at Mimura’s then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:05.49,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:08.82,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Ok.  “This is the real Mimura.  I will do my best!”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:11.82,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,Wow. That wasn’t funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:14.55,[Mimura],,0,0,0,,That was me making a declaration!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.96,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Miss Rola, is this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.51,[Rola],,0,0,0,,This is better than the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:23.20,[Rola],,0,0,0,,It has two phrases and feels fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:22.43,[Mimura],,0,0,0,,It has two phrases so it’s ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.20,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.83,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Let’s look at Amano’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:25.64,[Amano],,0,0,0,,Mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:31.37,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Here.  “I am starting Twitter.  This is the real me.  I am 43 years old and I like cooking and female broadcasters.”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:36.34,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Really good! Totally not ordinary at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.37,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Ok, let’s look at Udo’s as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:42.22,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,“Amano~!  It’s the real me!”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.58,[Amano],,0,0,0,,Why are you tweeting at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:49.22,[Amano],,0,0,0,,Just tell me here.  Don’t tweet at this distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:50.59,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.43,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Hoto’s.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:57.53,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,“I’m tweeting after a long while.  I want to be kind.”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.63,[Hotohara],,0,0,0,,This sort of thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.93,[Hotohara],,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:03.64,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Now, Otake’s, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:05.24,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,With Otake’s style.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:07.41,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,“I will start.  I will start?”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:09.71,[Amano],,0,0,0,,He already quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:12.11,[Mimura],,0,0,0,,{\an3}Your premise is that you’re quitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:15.58,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,I feel self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:18.62,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:21.89,[Rola],typeset,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(43,392)}Everyone, {\alpha&HFF&\t(850,200,\alpha&H00&)}\N\N\Ndon’t be like Mr. Matsumoto, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:27.63,Caption Wizard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(510,315)}A bad example.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:26.10,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,I feel this feeling of rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:29.14,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,I feel like I’m going to get a rashes as a reaction to all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:31.50,[Otake],,0,0,0,,It’s annoying to have to think up something!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:35.00,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,I don’t like how even something like this feels like work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:43.61,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,{\pos(259,335)}We have already started with this
