Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:44.78,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Are there any?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.08,0:22:49.55,[Matsumoto],typeset,0,0,0,,Sorry, I’d like to tweet, {\alpha&HFF&\t(510,0,\alpha&H00&)\fnFrankRuehl\c&H000000&\bord1\shad0\b1}“I have retired.”
