Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.87,0:24:35.90,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Miss Rola didn’t want to just teach how to use Twitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.90,0:24:40.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The real subject of this episode will now be presented to the members.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.36,0:24:45.83,[Rola],Typeset,0,0,0,,Now, we will have a competition on who will get the most {\c&H030005&\4c&HB53DEC&}followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.17,0:24:50.00,[Mimura],,0,0,0,,{\pos(496,293)}We do these frequently?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.00,0:24:52.60,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,How long should we do this?
