Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.71,0:24:58.18,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Longer than one week, but first, just one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.18,0:25:00.38,[Miyasako],,0,0,0,,Does something happen if you get last place?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.38,0:25:02.91,[Rola],typeset,0,0,0,,There will be a batsu game for the last place!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.62,0:25:05.12,[Miyasako],,0,0,0,,Good thing I’ve been doing Twitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.12,0:25:08.59,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Miyasako has already been doing Twitter, so he’s not part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.59,0:25:10.49,[Rola],typeset,0,0,0,Swipe DownLeft,{\move(360,390,150,500,1500,1600)}But Mr. Otohara will be part of it!
