Dialogue: 3,0:25:50.20,0:25:53.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The members begin to tweet to Rola.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:57.00,0:25:58.77,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Oh, I got something from Mr. Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:58.59,0:25:59.78,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,You got something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.78,0:26:04.71,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Here.  “I’m a little hungry.  What’s good for this sort of thing?”, he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.17,0:26:08.99,[Amano],,0,0,0,,Uh oh! Uh oh! Why did she say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.81,0:26:11.90,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Why do you seem to have this thing against Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.95,0:26:16.72,[Udo],,0,0,0,,Here I go. I’m going to do it! Everyone’s going to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.72,0:26:23.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Once Rola retweets the members’ tweets to her followers, reactions to the members’ tweets come in quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.13,0:26:28.40,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,We have a reply to Mr. Matsumoto from a regular person!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.19,0:26:30.95,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,“Is this the real Ma-chan?”
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.39,0:26:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.47,0:26:34.54,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.54,0:26:36.31,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Let’s reply to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.63,0:26:42.59,[Amano],,0,0,0,,Wow, that guy’s lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.55,0:26:45.92,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,Would it be bad if I was abusive towards him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.42,0:26:48.42,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,What sort of abuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.52,0:26:51.42,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,He said “Is this the real Ma-chan?”  Why would you reply to that with abuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.42,0:26:54.03,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,I just did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.03,0:26:56.03,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,To “Is this the real Mr. Matsumoto”:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.62,0:27:00.37,Tweet Text,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs30\pos(116,226)}The real one. I want to be kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.37,0:27:04.35,[Hotohara],,0,0,0,,My thing.  “I want to be kind,” that’s my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.80,0:27:07.64,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,{\pos(529,387)}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.13,0:27:07.64,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,You didn’t say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.01,0:27:14.01,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,{\pos(322,330)}Miyasako said before that “-tion” is only his thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.96,0:27:10.81,[Miyasako],,0,0,0,,I said the “-tion” thing is only my thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.81,0:27:14.01,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,You didn’t say “I want to be kind” is only your thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.54,0:27:14.01,[Hotohara],,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,283)}But, wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.01,0:27:17.68,[Hotohara],,0,0,0,,isn’t that the rule?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.92,0:27:17.68,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.68,0:27:21.29,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,I just, didn’t really understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.29,0:27:27.43,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,351)}For people who don’t know what’s going on here they must be like
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.55,0:27:27.43,[Matsumoto],,0,0,0,,“What the hell is Matsumoto saying?!”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.43,0:27:29.06,[Rola],,0,0,0,,I got tweets as well, saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.06,0:27:32.33,[Rola],,0,0,0,,{\fs34\1c&HFFAC00&\4c&H9925DD&\clip(37,317,39,400)\t(0,1750,\clip(37,317,750,400)}“Rola, you’re following too many fake accounts!”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.58,0:27:34.45,[Amano],,0,0,0,,We’re not fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.53,0:27:37.52,[Amano],,0,0,0,,We’re not fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.33,0:27:38.67,Caption Wizard,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,312)}They’re not trusted yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.67,0:27:42.97,[Mimura],,0,0,0,,If you say “They’re real,” that would increase our followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.36,0:27:42.17,[Miyasako],,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.03,0:27:42.97,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,It’s going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.15,0:27:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.38,0:27:47.01,[Udo],,0,0,0,,Wow, Mr. Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.31,0:27:51.58,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Otake is already at 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.89,0:27:55.38,[Mimura],,0,0,0,,They trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.54,0:27:56.34,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.86,0:28:00.19,[Amano],,0,0,0,,Wow, it went up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.54,0:28:02.45,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,It went right up to 460.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.08,0:28:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,500, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.88,0:28:13.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The number of followers is already increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.70,0:28:19.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The members are embarking on a one week experience never done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.11,0:28:22.88,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Ok, everyone, good luck on your one week!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.88,0:28:26.08,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Your followers will decrease if you don’t tweet, so tweet everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.08,0:28:30.26,[Rola],,0,0,0,,And if I see them and think they’re good, I’ll retweet them!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.85,0:28:30.26,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.26,0:28:32.25,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,So that means that that will increase your followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.56,0:28:35.43,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Ok, bye everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.86,0:28:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re leaving just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.71,0:28:43.14,[Rola],,0,0,0,,Bye, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.80,0:28:46.57,[Hamada],,0,0,0,,Good luck on your one week!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.90,0:28:54.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone’s beginning Twitter now starts to create a stir!
