Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.16,0:29:17.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What caption will Otake add regarding Miyasako’s unique style of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.40,0:29:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s sent.
