Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.68,0:37:49.92,[Otake],,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.92,0:37:54.95,[Mimura],,0,0,0,,But {\alpha&HFF&\t(1785,200,\alpha&H00&)}unless you see more of the reaction first…
